Title : Muhamet Vila
Text : '''Muhamet (Bet) Vila''' (born 1928) was an [[Albanians|Albanian]] [[Association football|footballer]] who played his entire professional career as defender for [[Dinamo Tirana]] football club. Paired with Xhevdet Shaqiri he formed the backbone of the defense for a Dinamo team that went on to win 6 league titles in the 1950s. Vila served as head coach of [[Besa Kavajë]] in the 1970s and helped lead the club to 2 Albania Cup finals appearances and to the final of the Balkan Cup tournament of 1971. He was capped 3 times with the [[Albania National Football Team]].<ref>{{cite web|url=http://eu-football.info/_player.php?id=22220|title=Player Database}}</ref>

